{"tid":494391,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS1兩隻遊戲 跪求Game名","createTime":"2017-12-09T14:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T19:30:32.000Z","uid":160926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"47d5c502cbf08f89222e1e0bc4bbf045ff6364d5","tid":494391,"uid":160926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:35:06.000Z","msg":"細細個好中意同阿哥玩兩隻ps1嘅game依家好想玩番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望各位神巴神絲 可以解答到我<br />\n<br />\n第一隻game<br />\n係槍game黎 真人風 可以插槍玩 會自動走場景 冇得自己行<br />\n每過一個scene就會自動幫妳hide係牆後面<br />\n要禁個制企起身出去可以射<br />\n無記錯只要一縮番去就會幫你入彈<br />\n印象中主角係一男一女 d畫面有d sega風<br />\n連有咩大佬都唔記得啦 sorry呀:(<br />\n因為同house of the dead呀 typing of the dead果d王係個腦到撈亂曬 怕記錯<br />\n<br />\n第二隻game<br />\n印象中有四個角色 可以揀兩個用 <br />\n同第一隻game一樣都係真人風 我記我我好中意用個大隻佬<br />\n佢個特色係 佢可以執場景d道具黎用 <br />\n最記得係 佢入笠果陣可以拎側邊支棍黎打人<br />\n最深印象就係隻game好難玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同親阿哥玩唔夠兩章就輸<br />\n <br />\n我都知道好抽象 好希望有大神可以解答我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946e17a1919ec3b22ee02ead6e2a29162372bfb6","tid":494391,"uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"第2隻係咪有得坐入隻渣古咁撚樣嘅機器人？"},{"pid":"6898995c3b88f59ea991901405740cd99ddb7dd2","tid":494391,"uid":160926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第2隻係咪有得坐入隻渣古咁撚樣嘅機器人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係 係街頭風ge 但你果隻都好得意咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f7d0d11dac909924bd2a93dde87e51ad436d68","tid":494391,"uid":160926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第2隻係咪有得坐入隻渣古咁撚樣嘅機器人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5l4aku_0usA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5l4aku_0usA&d=I9q57khBnM14iE4uKaveFozu7PIJYhBZqlGrka